    "Name": "Lightning Attack Hovercraft",
    "UIName": "Lightning Attack Hovercraft (RL)",
    "Details": "<b>Name: <color=#85DBF6>Lightning Attack Hovercraft (RL)</color>\nArmor: <color=#85DBF6>Ferro-Fibrous</color>\tTechnology: <color=#85DBF6>Inner Sphere</color>\nMovement: <color=#85DBF6>11/17 (Hover)</color>\tEngine: <color=#85DBF6>210 Fusion</color></b>\n\nThe Lightning, a reconnaissance hovercraft designed for the Star League, was used to take down slow BattleMechs and vehicles. Commanders would combine multiple Lightnings to crush hostile lines, using their maneuverability to break formations.\n\nSpecifically designed to exploit the weaknesses of Stealth Armor-equipped 'Mechs at close range, this Word of Blake variant carries seven Rocket Launcher 15s and two Anti-Missile Systems for added protection.",
